OL,3,CMet Police to double use of live
OL,4,Cfacial recognition amid budget cuts
OL,6,FBritain's largest police force will
OL,7,Fmore than double its use of live
OL,8,Ffacial recognition as part of a major
OL,9,Frestructure, while reducing its number
OL,10,Fof officers.
OL,12,FThe Metropolitan Police restructure,
OL,13,Fwhich follows a #260 million budget
OL,14,Fshortfall, will see 1,400 officer
OL,15,Fpositions and 300 staff jobs cut.
OL,17,FThe Met announced on Thursday that as
OL,18,Fpart of its plans, live facial
OL,19,Frecognition would now be used up to
OL,20,Ften times per week over five days.
