OL,3,CMet Police to double use of live
OL,4,Cfacial recognition amid budget cuts
OL,6,FIt is currently allowed to be used
OL,7,Ffour times across two days.
OL,9,FMetropolitan Police Commissioner, Sir
OL,10,FMark Rowley, said the technology would
OL,11,Fonly be used to look for serious
OL,12,Fcriminals, like registered sex
OL,13,Foffenders.
OL,15,F"We routinely put it out there and
OL,16,Fcapture multiple serious offenders in
OL,17,Fone go, many of whom have committed
OL,18,Fserious offences against women or
OL,19,Fchildren, or people who are wanted for
OL,20,Farmed robbery," he said.
