OL,3,CMet Police to double use of live
OL,4,Cfacial recognition amid budget cuts
OL,6,F"It's a fantastic piece of technology.
OL,7,FIt's very responsibly used and that's
OL,8,Fwhy most of the public support it."
OL,10,FMet Police revealed more than 1,000
OL,11,Farrests had been made using live
OL,12,Ffacial recognition since the
OL,13,Ftechnology was introduced, with nearly
OL,14,F800 of those arrests resulting in a
OL,15,Fcharge or caution.
OL,17,FBut Liberty's policy and campaigns
OL,18,Fofficer Charlie Whelton said
OL,19,Fincreasing the use was "incredibly
OL,20,Fconcerning" as there was a lack of
OL,21,Fregulation.
