OL,11,FAs part of the overhaul to the Met,
OL,12,Fthe public order crime team will also
OL,13,Fbe bulked up with an additional 15
OL,14,Fofficers, partly to help with a rise
OL,15,Fin protest-related crimes.
OL,17,FThere will also be more officers
OL,18,Fworking in neighbourhood teams to help
OL,19,Ftackle street crime including phone
OL,20,Fthefts, anti-social behaviour and
OL,21,Fshoplifting.
