OL,6,FRetailers had warned police that
OL,7,Fflagship high streets, such as Oxford
OL,8,FStreet in London's West End, were at
OL,9,Frisk without urgent national action on
OL,10,Fcrime.
OL,12,FShoplifting hit a record high in 2024
OL,13,Fwith more than 500,000 offences
OL,14,Frecorded.
OL,16,FThe West End will receive an extra 80
OL,17,Fofficers as part of the plan, while
OL,18,Fthe London areas of Brixton, Kingston,
OL,19,FEaling, Finsbury Park, Southwark and
OL,20,FSpitalfields will share 90 more
OL,21,Fofficers.
